<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>A KA HRUAINAK KIP AH CH356</title>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Lungnem nuntha tuukhal zoh tuah! Tidai pawng a dir lioah, Rawltam
 tihal mi kal u si, Ramtha chungah kal u si.

[C1]
   A hmuhsak lam kan zulh lai (lam kan zulh lai) Ahmuhsak lam kan zulh
   lai (lam kan zulh lai) Hal-le-lu-jah, Hal-le-lu-jah, Khua zakip ah kan
   zulh lai.

[V2]
 Nunnak kutka a lutmi lawng, Pathian nih a hlawm hna lai, Amah a lu a
 hlohnak in, Nunnak kha a kan pek cang.

[C2]
   A hmuhsak lam kan zulh lai (lam kan zulh lai) Ahmuhsak lam kan zulh
   lai (lam kan zulh lai) Hal-le-lu-jah, Hal-le-lu-jah, Khua zakip ah kan
   zulh lai.

[V3]
 Nunnak kawm ah him in a lut, A penmi tuu kha kan si, Amah kha Pathian
 a hngalh bang, Kannih zong a kan hngalh ve.

[C3]
   A hmuhsak lam kan zulh lai (lam kan zulh lai) Ahmuhsak lam kan zulh
   lai (lam kan zulh lai) Hal-le-lu-jah, Hal-le-lu-jah, Khua zakip ah kan
   zulh lai.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>356</hymn_number>
</song>